    "title": "Usalama na Utii",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "usalama na utii",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Kitabu cha Uzima ni rekodi ya kiungu inayojumuisha majina ya wale wanaomilikiwa na Mungu na watakaopokea uzima wa milele (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:12\">Ufunuo 20:12</a>). Wazo la kuondoa jina kutoka Kitabu cha Uzima linaweza kuibua maswali kuhusu kama wokovu unaweza kupotea (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:5\">Ufunuo 3:5</a>). Je, Agano Jipya halisemi kwamba wokovu wa waumini ni salama?</p><p>Agano Jipya linatoa maneno mengi ya faraja (kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:27-John10:30\">Yohana 10:27–30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:13\">1 Wakorintho 10:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:18-Heb6:20\">Waebrania 6:18–20</a>). Lakini pia linatoa maonyo makali (kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:6\">Yohana 15:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:6-1Cor10:12\">1 Wakorintho 10:6–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:4-Heb6:8\">Waebrania 6:4–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:4-Rev2:5\">Ufunuo 2:4–5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:11\">3:11</a>). Mara nyingi hatupendi na tunakwepa maonyo haya kwa sababu yanatufanya tuhisi kutokuwa salama. Hata hivyo, wasiwasi huu kuhusu usalama ndio hasa sababu waandishi wa Agano Jipya walitoa maonyo haya. Walisisitiza umuhimu wa utii, uaminifu, na uvumilivu.</p><p>Wito huu wa utii haukuwa mpya. Mungu aliwaita watu wa Israeli mara kwa mara kuwa waaminifu (kwa mfano, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:1-Gen12:2\">Mwanzo 12:1–2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:1-Gen15:18\">15:1–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:16-Gen22:18\">22:16–18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:13-Gen28:14\">28:13–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:19-1Sam12:25\">1 Samweli 12:19–25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:10-1Sam15:11\">15:10–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:16-1Sam28:19\">28:16–19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:11-2Sam7:16\">2 Samweli 7:11–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:4-1Kgs9:9\">1 Wafalme 9:4–9</a>). Ahadi na unabii wote wa Mungu hutegemea uaminifu na utii (tazama hasa <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:7-Jer18:10\">Yeremia 18:7–10</a>). Mtume Paulo alielewa kwamba kutotii kwa Israeli kulisababisha baadhi yao &quot;kutengwa&quot; na watu wa Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:17\">Warumi 11:17</a>). Aliwaonya Wakristo wasio Wayahudi (Mataifa) wasiwe na ujasiri kupita kiasi kuhusu nafasi yao (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:13-Rom11:32\">Warumi 11:13–32</a>). Ahadi ya Mungu inabaki ile ile, lakini kutotii kwa binadamu husababisha hukumu. Usalama wa kweli unatokana na utii wa unyenyekevu na kutegemea Mungu.</p><p>Wakati wa Agano Jipya, kuwa Mkristo ilikuwa kazi ngumu na hatari. Kitabu cha Ufunuo kinatoa tumaini kwa Wakristo, hata wanapokabiliwa na tishio la kifo. Tumaini hili linakuja pamoja na maonyo kuhusu hukumu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:8\">Ufunuo 21:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:27\">27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:15\">22:15</a>). Wito wa uaminifu na utiifu ni mada kuu katika Ufunuo (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:5\">2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10-Rev2:11\">10–11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:16-Rev2:17\">16–17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:26-Rev2:29\">26–29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:2\">3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:12\">12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:17-Rev3:19\">17–19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:21-Rev3:22\">21–22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:14\">7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:9-Rev13:10\">13:9–10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:12\">12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:15\">16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:4\">18:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:12\">20:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:7\">21:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:3\">22:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:7\">7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:11-Rev22:12\">11–12</a>). Agano Jipya linathibitisha kwamba kwa msaada wa Mungu, Wakristo waaminifu watavumilia hadi mwisho (tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:6\">Waebrania 13:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:25\">Yakobo 1:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:10\">Ufunuo 3:10</a>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:1\">Mwanzo 15:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen15:13-Gen15:16\">13–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:22-1Sam12:25\">1 Samweli 12:22–25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs9:4-1Kgs9:9\">1 Wafalme 9:4–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer18:7-Jer18:10\">Yeremia 18:7–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:27-John10:30\">Yohana 10:27–30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:6\">15:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:13-Rom11:32\">Warumi 11:13–32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:6-1Cor10:12\">1 Wakorintho 10:6–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:4-Heb6:8\">Waebrania 6:4–8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:18-Heb6:20\">18–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:6\">13:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:25\">Yakobo 1:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:5\">Ufunuo 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10-Rev2:11\">10–11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:16-Rev2:17\">16–17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:5\">3:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:10-Rev3:12\">10–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:4\">18:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:12\">20:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:7-Rev21:8\">21:7–8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:11-Rev22:12\">22:11–12</a></p>",
